videos.description: On the third snap of the game, Boise State goes deep when Brett Rypien finds Jeremy McNichols for a 76-yard hookup to the end zone, giving the Broncos the early lead.
videos.headline: McNichols jump-starts Boise State with 76-yard TD

videos.description: Boise State makes it two touchdowns in two drives, this time a 12-yard touchdown pass from Brett Rypien to Thomas Sperbeck, making it 14-0 Broncos less than four minutes into the game.
videos.headline: Rypien strikes again for another Boise State touchdown

videos.description: Tyler Rausa 32 yd FG BLOCKED blocked by Dayan Lake  Dayan Lake return for 25 yds to the BYU 47
videos.headline: T. Rausa 32 yd FG BLOCKED,blocked by Dayan Lake,D. Lake return for 25 yds

videos.description: BYU gets a much needed spark when Fred Warner makes the interception and then goes through a plethora of tackles, all while tip-toeing down the sideline, to dive for the end zone and finish off the outstanding pick-six.
videos.headline: Warner fights through all the tackles for incredible BYU pick-six

videos.description: With BYU facing a fourth-and-19 and punting from out of its end zone, punter Jonny Linehan runs it instead and barely gets out of the end zone to escape the safety.
videos.headline: 4th-and-19 from your own goal line isn't a good time for a fake punt

videos.description: Dayan Lake pulls in the deflected pass and then races down the sidelines to the house scoring BYU's second pick-six of the game and giving the Cougars their first lead of the night at 17-14.
videos.headline: Lake scores BYU's second pick-six of the game

videos.description: Jeremy McNichols run for 20 yds to the BoiSt 41 Jeremy McNichols fumbled, forced by Kai Nacua, recovered by BYU Handsome Tanielu
videos.headline: BYU forces 3rd turnover of the 1st half

videos.description: After throwing two pick-sixes, Brett Rypien strikes back with a perfect toss to Cedrick Wilson, who makes the diving catch in the end zone, giving Boise State back the lead in spectacular fashion heading into halftime.
videos.headline: Fingertip diving TD catch puts Boise State ahead going into the half

videos.description: Taysom Hill pass incomplete to Nick Kurtz
videos.headline: BYU almost gets the Hail Mary before the end of the half

videos.description: BYU almost converts desperation heave before halftime
videos.headline: BYU almost converts desperation heave before halftime

videos.description: Taysom Hill airs it out deep where Mitchell Juergens makes the diving grab between a pair of Boise State defenders for the highlight-reel play. Mitchell was ruled down at the one-yard line and BYU would punch it in on the next play.
videos.headline: Juergens makes the ridiculous diving grab to set up BYU TD

videos.description: Taysom Hill run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.headline: T. Hill run for 1 yd for a TD

videos.description: Brett Rypien pass complete to Thomas Sperbeck for 5 yds Thomas Sperbeck fumbled, forced by Fred Warner, recovered by BYU Troy Warner
videos.headline: BYU defense forces 5th Boise State turnover

videos.description: Brett Rypien pass complete to Jake Knight for 46 yds to the BYU 4 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: B. Rypien pass to J. Knight for 46 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Boise State goes 90 yards in 10 plays, capped off with a Jeremy McNichols touchdown from four yards out to put Boise State back in front at 28-27.
videos.headline: McNichols punches it in to cap off 10-play Boise State drive

videos.description: BYU lines up for a late go-ahead field goal but Boise State blocks the kick to preserve a dramatic 28-27 win.
videos.headline: Boise State wins on dramatic blocked field goal

videos.description: Taysom Hill pass incomplete to Nick Kurtz
videos.headline: BYU attempts hail Mary as time expires in the game
